Interface HealthConstants.FoodIntake

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HealthConstants.Common, HealthConstants.DiscreteMeasurement
    Enclosing class:
    HealthConstants

    public static interface HealthConstants.FoodIntake
extends HealthConstants.DiscreteMeasurement
    This interface defines constants for food intake data of user.

      • CALORIE

        static final String CALORIE
        Total calories of the meal in kilocalories.

        • Mandatory
        • Type: float
        • Value range: 0 ~ 99999

        Calorie intake can be calculated as shown below. 
            Calories = FoodIntake.AMOUNT * FoodInfo.DEFAULT_NUMBER_OF_SERVING_UNIT
